Class GameInvoker

java.lang.Object
com.project.Gameplay.GameInvoker
public class GameInvoker extends Object
Central invoker used to execute game commands and record event logs. Records a log entry before and after executing each command.

      public ReportHelper createReportHelper(ArrayList<Player> players)

      Parameters:
